{"tid":1577440,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"近期搭地鐵盡量唔好企肉餅位","createTime":"2019-09-17T16:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T19:34:21.000Z","uid":232671,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6c528aee13780655242eb80b7c816f989e8c2132","tid":1577440,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"純粹陰謀論, 唔啱睇請上一頁<br />\n<br />\n9月16日信報先講話&quot;北京底線是不能破壞機場及鐵路&quot;<br />\n9月17日就火車出軌<br />\n<br />\n有冇咁啱呀?? 我就唔信啦!!! 仲有, 個headline &quot;北京底線是不能破壞機場及鐵路&quot; 都勁古怪啦!!<br />\n<br />\n重點: 我相信賤招陸續有黎, 呢類型恐怖襲擊唔會就咁就停...<br />\n今次好彩係東鐵線, 露天, ... 但其他線呢? 如果班賤人搞其他線, 而有手足不幸企正肉餅位...咁就真係夾死都似......近呢兩星期靠中間些少企啦...可以的話盡量坐其他交通工具.....<br />\n<br />\n天祐港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[完]"},{"pid":"0d07373885c90c17991d265d32222d7c261b3c1c","tid":1577440,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:43:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"50a758f0234a236bd434beda7ed6b95cfe16cb3f","tid":1577440,"uid":169048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:48:18.000Z","msg":"睇多啲信報 預知敵人點襲擊香港"},{"pid":"e79a0efd9ceff3f7d34804b692deafaf0716af8b","tid":1577440,"uid":70685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"50a758f0234a236bd434beda7ed6b95cfe16cb3f","tid":1577440,"uid":169048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:48:18.000Z","msg":"睇多啲信報 預知敵人點襲擊香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:50:20.000Z","msg":"呢個位慢駛姐 行得快企咩位都死啦"},{"pid":"91e886eee186d0ba2b5d52137e73cdb9cbbfbc0e","tid":1577440,"uid":50676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:51:43.000Z","msg":"仲搭港鐵？"},{"pid":"ec8c386e0375d1a17159d974d65f1e6dcdd782aa","tid":1577440,"uid":68080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":